WorkflowInfo.Details: This process monitors the availability of a URL, by searching for a specific phrase that indicates the site as available. In case the site is detected as down, a set of activities is performed. You can schedule this process to run on an hourly basis to monitor your top websites, and alert the relevant personnel in case of unavailability.
